nodes.text: Tikaroo was a town located on the planet Devaron. The town was composed of a few small stilt houses, most of which were one or two stories tall. Tikaroo was surrounded by jungle. Luke Skywalker landed in Tikaroo after his BTL-A4 Y-wing assault starfighter/bomber was damaged, and from there he headed for the Jedi Temple of Eedit.
